The 5th Edition of Systems Analysis and Design continues to offer a 

hands-on 
approach to SA&D while focusing on the core set of skills that all 

analysts 
must possess.  Building on their experience as professional systems 

analysts 
and award-winning teachers, authors Dennis, Wixom, and Roth capture 

the 
experience of developing and analyzing systems in a way that 

students can 
understand and apply. With Systems Analysis and Design, 5th Edition, 

students 
will leave the course with experience that is a rich foundation for 

further 
work as a systems analyst.
